        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Securing Our Students Act</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes local educational agencies and nonpublic schools to use certain COVID-19 emergency relief funds, services, or assistance for school safety uses, that is improving school conditions for student learning by planning and designing school buildings and facilities, installing infrastructure, providing safety education, and implementing technology or other measures that strengthen security on school premises.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
